      <PrimaryExemptPurposeTxt>JAMAICA CAPITAL CORPORATION ("JCC") WAS FORMED FOR THE EXCLUSIVE PURPOSE OF BENEFITING, SUPPORTING AND FURTHERING THE GOALS OF GREATER JAMAICA DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION ("GJDC"), A PUBLICLY SUPPORTED 501 (C) (3) ORGANIZATION. JCC'S ACTIVITIES HAVE FURTHERED GJDC'S CHARITABLE PURPOSES AND SERVED TO LESSEN THE BURDENS OF THE GOVERNMENT.</PrimaryExemptPurposeTxt>
      <ProgramSrvcAccomplishmentGrp>
        <DescriptionProgramSrvcAccomTxt>JCC'S EFFORTS HAVE BEEN FOCUSED ON THE DEVELOPMENT OF SEVERAL, LARGE-SCALE UNDERUTILIZED SITES IN THE AREA IMMEDIATELY ADJACENT TO THE AIRTRAIN/LIRR STATION. ON ONE SITE, JCC PURCHASED PROPERTY CREATING A SIGNIFICANT ASSEMBLAGE. JCC AND GJDC SOLD THE PARCELS TO BE DEVELOPED AS A 700,000 SQUARE FOOT 669 UNIT MIXED-INCOME HOUSING AND RETAIL PROJECT. THE TRANSACTION CLOSED IN MAY 2015. THE BUILDINGS ON THE SITE ARE NOW DEMOLISHED AND THE PROJECT IS IN CONSTRUCTION. THE PROJECT HAS CATALYZED OTHER ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT ACTIVITY IN THE STATION AREA AND ELSEWHERE IN JAMAICA.</DescriptionProgramSrvcAccomTxt>
